data.description: Fantastic 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home with open concept living. Main floor boasts formal living and dining rooms, and den that opens to the spacious kitchen with tons of cabinet space and stainless steel appliances. Top floor bedrooms including large primary suite and loft area ideal for in-home office. Fenced backyard, patio and fire pit ideal for entertaining. Move-In Ready!
